# Git Sync Dev

Lightweight push to `origin/dev` without merging to `main`.

## Steps

1. Run `git status`, `git diff`, `git log --oneline -3`
2. Ensure on `dev`: `git checkout dev && git pull origin dev`
3. If uncommitted changes exist, ask whether to commit first or run `/git-release` for the full flow
4. Push: `git push -u origin dev`
5. Report branch status and latest commit SHA

## When to use

- Work-in-progress on `dev` that is not ready for `main`
- For release to production branch, use `/git-release` instead
